lead_paragraph: Newcomers Townley Haas, Olivia Smoliga and Lilly King all punched their tickets to the Rio Games upstaging some of the biggest names in U.S. swimming on Tuesday, as a wave of fresh faces washed over the U.S. Olympic trials.

headline.print_headline: Newcomers Take Spotlight at U.S. Olympic Trials
